text: Robert George White (born 15 September 1995) is an English cricketer who plays for Middlesex County Cricket Club. A wicket-keeper, who is a right-handed batsman, who also bowls right-arm medium pace. He made his first-class debut for Loughborough MCC University against Hampshire County Cricket Club in April 2015. He made his List A debut for Middlesex against Australia on 9 June 2018, during Australia's tour of England.
